quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,119,Thumma 'Inna Rabbaka Lilladhīna `Amilū As-Sū'a Bijahālatin Thumma Tābū Min Ba`di Dhālika Wa 'Aşlaĥū 'Inna Rabbaka Min Ba`dihā Laghafūrun Raĥīmun
  16,120,Inna 'Ibrāhīma Kāna 'Ummatan Qānitāan Lillāhi Ĥanīfāan Wa Lam Yaku Mina Al-Mushrikīna
  16,121,Shākirāan Li'n`umihi Ajtabāhu Wa Hadāhu 'Ilá Şirāţin Mustaqīm
  16,122,Wa 'Ātaynāhu Fī Ad-Dunyā Ĥasanatan Wa 'Innahu Fī Al-'Ākhirati Lamina Aş-Şāliĥīna
  16,123,Thumma 'Awĥaynā 'Ilayka 'Ani Attabi` Millata 'Ibrāhīma Ĥanīfāan Wa Mā Kāna Mina Al-Mushrikīna
  16,124,Innamā Ju`ila As-Sabtu `Alá Al-Ladhīna Akhtalafū Fīhi Wa 'Inna Rabbaka Layaĥkumu Baynahum Yawma Al-Qiyāmati Fīmā Kānū Fīhi Yakhtalifūna
  16,125,Ad`u 'Ilá Sabīli Rabbika Bil-Ĥikmati Wa Al-Maw`ižati Al-Ĥasanati Wa Jādilhum Bi-Atī Hiya 'Aĥsanu 'Inna Rabbaka Huwa 'A`lamu Biman Đalla `An Sabīlihi Wa Huwa 'A`lamu Bil-Muhtadīna
  16,126,Wa 'In `Āqabtum Fa`āqibū Bimithli Mā `Ūqibtum Bihi Wa La'in Şabartum Lahuwa Khayrun Lilşşābirīna
  16,127,Wa Aşbir Wa Mā Şabruka 'Illā Billāhi Wa Lā Taĥzan `Alayhim Wa Lā Taku Fī Đayqin Mimmā Yamkurūna
  16,128,Inna Allāha Ma`a Al-Ladhīna Attaqaw Wa Al-Ladhīna Hum Muĥsinūna